      "content": "that's a really good start. it definitely hits the moral angle well. can you expand on that a bit more? specifically, can you help me write a section that breaks down why the \"meritocracy\" argument—the idea that people just get what they deserve based on hard work—is actually a flawed way to look at this? i want to show how that logic ignores the actual reality of how race and wealth work together.",
